 blessings be upon him. Afterwards, he called out, \u201cO Allah, have mercy upon me and Muhammad and do not share Your mercy with anyone else!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cDo\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35399,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/03\/18\/tell-your-brother\/","url_meta":{"origin":13459,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Brotherhood: Tell your brothers that you love them","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Miqdam ibn Ma\u2019di reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen a man loves his brother, let him tell him that he loves him.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 5124 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0642\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062f\u0650\u064a \u0643\u064e\u0631\u0650\u0628\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9947,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/24\/give-gifts-love-one-another\/","url_meta":{"origin":13459,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Gifts: Give each other gifts, you will love each other","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGive each other gifts and you will love each other.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 594 Grade:\u00a0Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to\u00a0Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0644\u064a\u0647 \u0648\u0633\u0644\u0645 \u0642\u0627\u0644\u200f \u062a\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u062a\u064e\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0628\u064f\u0651\u0648\u0627 594 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062f\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0641\u0631\u062f \u0644\u0644\u0628\u062e\u0627\u0631\u064a 3\/1047 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u062d\u062f\u062b \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u062d\u062c\u0631\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23449,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/07\/12\/honor-love-sake-of-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":13459,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Love: Allah honors those who love each other","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 12, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA servant does not love another servant for the sake of Allah Almighty but that Allah will honor him.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 8601 Grade: Jayyid (very good) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0623\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2531,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/26\/love-hate-moderation\/","url_meta":{"origin":13459,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Moderation: Love and hate in moderation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 26, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cLove whom you love mildly, perhaps he will become hateful to you someday. Hate whom you hate mildly, perhaps he will become your beloved someday.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1997 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33786,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/11\/20\/lineage-learn-family-history\/","url_meta":{"origin":13459,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Lineage: Learn your family history to solidify familial ties","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cLearn your lineages to solidify your family ties. Verily, keeping family ties causes love among the kinship, enriches the wealth, and increases the lifespan.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1979